		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">and lvl from 17 to 27 :)<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: and lvl from 17 to 27 :)";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Sat, Aug 18th 11:04 AM2001 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=99814705637282&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=4&mid=99814705637282&num=0&post=1&replyto=99814705637282"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=99814705637282></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></a><b><span id=></span></b>
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Anonymous&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Hello ! here is a compilation of what I read or hear from other players and done !<br />For lvl17 to 27 : (I posted one also for lvl1 to 17).<br />First of all, I am french so excuse my english if there are some errors ;)&#8230;<br />_ When you reach lvl 17 go directly to Lake Rathe, ask for a bind in the arena and camp the hermit who is at the far end of the zone : he is really good xp and descent loot (lot of water ;) ) ; be carefull he hit very badly so keep your restoration song in hotkey ! You can stay on him until lvl20 easely. In this zone, a very usefull thing to do is trying to get an Opaline Helm from deepwater goblins, make a /shout and ask if somebody is killing them, if so ask if you can loot the helm wich is « no drop », normaly campers will destroy it or let it on the corpse so it will be no problem to have it :). This helm is a part of the quest of the lambent helm ! A very good thing is also going to improve your brass and wind skills (wind if you get your invis song from erudite&#8217;s town) in the arena ! Just enter it before you leave to eat or something else, then play the brass or wind song with an instrument, this is an easy way to make them better.<br />_ At lvl 20 I move to Gorge of king Xorb (zone north of EK), I go straight until 3 ways are in front of me and wait for minotaurs to pass by : kill them ! you will see quickly one with a horn in his hand, kill him more than ever ;) : you will loot the minotaur horn wich increase wind song by 15% ! and at lvl 20 it will be very usefull if you plan to start lambent armor quest (Cazic Thul, Guk&#8230;)!<br />_ Then I return to Lake rathe and I stay there until I reach 25. You can kill the aviak guard at diving board until you reach 21 then group or solo aviak trees (like 1k island or flame) until 25 (at 24 you can solo flame) ; at 21 I could solo 1k easely : just split the spawn with lull spell (8) then pull one with brusco DD (12) then Anthem(10), then largo mel bind (20) (replace by chain at 23) and finaly DDD (18), I made 1 bubble every 30 min ! Aviak guards are good xp and good loot too : runes, words and pp.<br />_ At 25 Lake Rathe will give you no or very slow xp&#8230;I move to Kelethin in Gfay to buy my lvl 26,27,28 songs, then I take the barge in BBmountains for Firiona Vie (Kunark). Ask for a bind near the bank (dont forget to buy a lot of food and drink before reaching Kunark), then follow the river to Lake of Ill Omen (be carefull to the spiders !). New playing area with a lot of people but also hundreds of mobs ! At 25 a lot of them will con low blue, follow the river then go south and stop near the ruines (just north of windmill), you can solo with the usual tactic (just take the mob near the border of the zone), try preferably goblins and sarnaks (better money and loots). You can also go and group in the sarnak fort (low but safe xp&#8230;). You will reach quickly 26. Mem fear song then try it with chain and brusco DD (12). Fear is dangerous song but very usefull when the group or you have big problems ;). At 26 make a group or enter one wich is going to Frontier Mountains (FM), you need to be full ! Just enter the zone and move until the descent. We kill a Giant ! (my first one ;)), and many others mobs wich con yellow or red : the xp is really good for a 6 people group (better than sarnak fort) ! I have to say the group was very good (1 druid, 1 monk, 1 ranger, 1 enchanter, 1 paladin and me ;)). If the group does&#8217;nt break lvl 27 is here !<br />I hope it will help the young bards ! Good luck all !<br /><br />Valaba Noirac<br />27 Bard on Karana<br />25 Bard on Therris T</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td></tr></table>
